                  </persName>
            . I am a lace-man; I live at Radcliffe-cross; I did live in Oxfordshire: I have known her five or six years; I never heard any thing amiss of her character before this; I dealt with her for hundreds of pounds; I have left cards of lace with her time after time; I always received them as I left them.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t17730421-2-person82">
                  Joseph
                   Witbridge
               <interp inst="t17730421-2-person82" type="surname" value="Witbridge"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17730421-2-person82" type="given" value="Joseph"></interp>
