                  </persName>
            . I live in Fleet-street; I am a silk morcer: I have known her four or five years.</p>
               <p>Q. What is her general character?</p>
               <p>Witbridge. I have not heard much of it; she has dealt with me, and always paid me honestly. I have not dealt with her this twelve-month past, as I know of.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t17730421-2-person83">
                  Eleanor
                   Ellway
               <interp inst="t17730421-2-person83" type="surname" value="Ellway"></interp>
